data.description:
This 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home feature quiet park-like living. Large deck to enjoy the outside and entertain. Two car *attached* garage perfect for Minnesota winters! End unit provides more privacy and no traffic in front. Maintenance free living and tons shared amenities including: pool, sport court, sand volleyball, and putput golf. Convenient location close to many walking trails and shopping.
** Price Reduction! Seller will consider contributing to buyers costs with an acceptable offer. Bring an offer!
